This paper is primarily focused on object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses domain adaptation and transfer learning, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in multimedia analysis (cs.MM) and the use of web images, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
